                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Choate</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-03-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 8, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay states that shippers have been advised in accordance with Mr. Choate’s
                    cablegram of the 7th instant.</p>
                <p>Directs that British foreign office be advised that Norton &amp; Son suggest the
                    danger of long continued confinement below hatches of a shipment of oil on the
                        <hi rend="italic">Mashona</hi>, resulting in spontaneous combustion and
                    destruction of ship and cargo.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
